@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (((v0 + 0.45 * v0 + 0.52) * tmp) - wp.sin((v0 + 0.49 * tmp + 0.47)))
    tmp = wp.abs((0.29 * wp.exp(tmp + 0.08)))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.abs(tmp))
    v0 = (((v0 + 0.69 + v1 + 0.80) / wp.exp(v1 + 0.26)) * (wp.exp(v2 + 0.55) / wp.sin(v1 + 0.57)))
    v1 = (wp.sin(v0) + (tmp * 0.50))
    data[tid] = v0
